vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to DCPG I, Inc. for the use of approximately 1,143 square feet of land to occupy, maintain and utilize a subsurface electrical vault meter under a portion of Wood Street right-of-way located near its intersection with Market Street - Revenue: General Fund $4,732.00 annually, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
